"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-16-The-firsts-of-all-three-Paris-Olympic-Games-1vhCikyiCxq-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Copied  This summer, Paris will become the world's second city after London to host the Summer Olympic Games three times. Paris has consistently surprised the world, with each Olympic Games pioneering in its own way. Let us take a trip down memory lane as we anticipate what Paris will bring us this time!  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"